00:12:31,050 --> 00:12:32,940
Arrange Her Highness
to go to Xiuwen Hall tomorrow.

282
00:12:33,530 --> 00:12:34,700
Notify Princess Royal in advance.

283
00:12:35,170 --> 00:12:36,010
Yes.

284
00:12:43,650 --> 00:12:44,580
I'll leave the rest

